node app.js encrypt --path /home/filipe/git/bifrost/thefolder --tarName assembly -p 'pass' --iv iv

node app.js decrypt --path /home/filipe/git/bifrost/assembly.tgz.enc -p 'pass' --iv iv -d ./extract2

First argv    The method that you want to use 
Methods avaiable: 
[
  'encrypt',
  'decrypt',
]

-p        The password to encrypt or descrypt some tar file 
--iv       The initial vector used to encrypt or descrypt some tar file
--path     The path where is the folder or the file that you want to use
-d        Destiny for your decrypted file